  "body": "> would be extra nice if user could specify param on CLI for how many blocks before epoch to generate next DAG. i.e. 300 blocks @ 12s ~ 1 hour before next epoch\n\nThis is very easy to implement by watching block number instead and generate next DAG when \n\n```\nethashDir := \"~/.ethash\"\ncurrentEpoch := currentBlock.Number/30000\nif currentBlock.Number % 30000 > X {\n  os.Remove(filepath.Join(ethashDir, dagFile(currentEpoch-1)\n  makeDAG(currentEpoch+1, ethashDir)\n}\n```\n",
