    "body": "Here's a bit maths for the console, assuming avgBlockSecs is set by user based on current generation rate, which may be lower than 12:\n\n```\n> avgBlockSecs = 7; epoch = 30000; (epoch - eth.blockNumber % epoch) * avgBlockSecs / 3600 + ' hours until epoch ' + (eth.blockNumber - eth.blockNumber % epoch + epoch)\n'4.7775 hours until epoch 360000'\n```\n",
